@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    Welcome to our privacy policy. Your privacy is important to us. This document explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our library services.
</p>

<h4>1. Data Collection</h4>
<p>
    We collect personal information such as your name, email address, and borrowed books data when you register and use our library services.
</p>

<h4>2. Data Usage</h4>
<p>
    We use your data to manage your library account, track borrowed books, communicate with you, and improve our services.
</p>

<h4>3. Cookies</h4>
<p>
    Our website uses cookies to enhance your user experience. You can adjust your cookie settings in your browser.
</p>

<h4>4. Third-Party Sharing</h4>
<p>
    We do not sell your data to third parties. However, we may share data with third-party service providers to process payments and improve our services.
</p>

<h4>5. Data Security</h4>
<p>
    We use SSL encryption and other security measures to protect your data.
</p>

<h4>6. Your Rights</h4>
<p>
    You have the right to access, update, and delete your personal data at any time. You can also contact us if you have any concerns.
</p>

<h4>7. Contact Us</h4>
<p>
    If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at [admin@gmail.com].
</p>
